Setps: 
    - Go to any page in website except home.
    - Write ../../../../../../../etc/passwd in url after page=.

Vulenrability name: File inclusion.
Vulenrability desc: The File Inclusion vulnerability allows an attacker to include a file,
                    usually exploiting a “dynamic file inclusion” mechanisms implemented in the target application.
                    The vulnerability occurs due to the use of user-supplied input without proper validation.

Ways to prevent vulenrability from happening:
    - Create a whitelist of acceptable filenames.